      "releaseNotes": "2.9.1\n- SDK updates, minor fixes and tweaks.\n\n2.9\n- Added a shadow point and indicator line in the Live + Street View modules.\n- Twilight Info Panel, Ephemeris: Dawn and Dusk times now show start and end.\n- Added a preference for the Time Machine Slider startup default.\n- New more realistic moon simulation in the Ephemeris with libration shown over the year.",
